== Tineḍwa == 

[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Blue_myrtle_berries_sardinia.JPG Cilmun], illa win rẓayen, illa win ẓiden. D aẓidan i tteɣẓaẓen imeksawen. Ur d-iwwi yara ad astuqqet yiwen deg učči ines, acku itbaddid (iḥettel), yerna isɣaray taɛebbuṭ.
 
